{"data":[{"date":"09:14 23/06","title":"Neymar gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Costa Rica","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/neymar-giai-thich-ly-do-bat-khoc-sau-tran-thang-costa-rica.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac sau khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Costa Rica v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa.\r\n</h2><h2>Neymar b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c sau tr\u1eadn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t \u0110T Brazil, nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Neymar lu\u00f4n \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi anh ch\u1ec9 v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i c\u00e0ng gia t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, sau khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 gi\u00fap <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-brazil-vs-costa-rica-463-189267.html\" target=\"_blank\">Brazil h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110T Costa Rica 2-0</span>, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c trong v\u00f2ng tay \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa r\u1ea5t l\u00f3n c\u1ee7a Neymar, khi anh qu\u1ef3 xu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f3c &ldquo;ngon l\u00e0nh&rdquo;. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m x\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y&rdquo; &ndash; Neymar chia s\u1ebb. &ldquo;L\u1eddi n\u00f3i ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n mua, ngay c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t con v\u1eb9t c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sao cho \u0111\u00fang th\u00ec \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Costa Rica\" title=\"Neymar chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Costa Rica\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/neymar-giai-thich-ly-do-bat-khoc-sau-tran-thang-costa-rica.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Costa Rica</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, s\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa, \u00fd ch\u00ed chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i, ngay c\u1ea3 l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c. Kh\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1, m\u00e0 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u1eadu l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1&rdquo; &ndash; Neymar chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Costa Rica.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HLV Tite th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Neymar ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1ea5t vui v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Neymar r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-20-costa-rica-421-189299.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/Philippe-Coutinho-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Brazil-vs-Costa-Rica-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-20-costa-rica-421-189299.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica</span><br>\r\nBrazil \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Costa Rica v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Costa Rica...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-costa-rica-461-189287.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/1_10.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-costa-rica-461-189287.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nT\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra bi\u1ebft bao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n song ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian th\u00eam gi\u1edd, Selecao m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Coutinho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi khai th\u00f4ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thiago-silva-noi-ve-man-khoc-nhe-cua-neymar-421-189307.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/thiago-silva-noi-ve-man-khoc-nhe-cua-neymar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thiago-silva-noi-ve-man-khoc-nhe-cua-neymar-421-189307.html\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0n &lsquo;kh\u00f3c nh\u00e8&rsquo; c\u1ee7a Neymar sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Costa Rica</span><br>\r\nSau khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1ed5i h\u1ed3i c\u00f2i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng kh\u00f3c n\u1ee9c n\u1edf. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec khi\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN) <span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"489","checkdouble":"189329"},{"date":"09:28 23/06","title":"\u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/duc-nhan-tin-buon-ngay-truoc-tran-gap-thuy-dien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1eb7p h\u1ecda khi trung v\u1ec7 Mats Hummels d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.\r\n</h2><h2>Hummels b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Mexico trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Joachim Low v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Die Mannschaft \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, khi trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Mats Hummels nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i. HLV Joachim Low cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf c\u1ed5 trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp h\u00f4m qua.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u1ebfn h\u00f4m nay, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec3n. Hummels \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ee1 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, v\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi gian b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ki\u1ec3u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c sau m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00eam. D\u00f9 sao, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Hummels l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mats Hummels d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t\" title=\"Mats Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 trong tr\u1eadn thua Mexico.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mats Hummels d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Joachim Low s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Antonio Rudiger, ho\u1eb7c Niklas Sule \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Jerome Boateng. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, v\u00ec thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110\u1ee9c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng suy gi\u1ea3m phong \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo; &ndash; Low l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf, sau khi trung v\u1ec7 Mats Hummels d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn: &ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i theo d\u00f5i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua, v\u00e0 h\u00e3y xem gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/duc-vs-thuy-dien-01h00-ngay-246-them-mot-bat-ngo-421-189328.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/duc-vs-thuy-dien-01h00-ngay-246-them-mot-bat-ngo.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/duc-vs-thuy-dien-01h00-ngay-246-them-mot-bat-ngo-421-189328.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (01h00 ng\u00e0y 24/6): Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd?</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i, Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c phong \u0111\u1ed9. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/miroslav-klose-nhung-ap-luc-cang-giup-duc-bung-no-manh-me-hon-421-189286.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/miroslav-klose-nhung-ap-luc-cang-giup-duc-bung-no-manh-me-hon.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/miroslav-klose-nhung-ap-luc-cang-giup-duc-bung-no-manh-me-hon-421-189286.html\">Miroslav Klose: Nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u00e0ng gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n</span><br>\r\nMiroslav Klose ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh khi l\u00e2m v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/khedira-duc-khong-muon-len-may-bay-tro-ve-nuoc-qua-som-421-189258.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/khedira-duc-khong-muon-len-may-bay-tro-ve-nuoc-qua-som.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/khedira-duc-khong-muon-len-may-bay-tro-ve-nuoc-qua-som-421-189258.html\">Khedira: \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm</span><br>\r\nSami Khedira ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"488","checkdouble":"189330"},{"date":"09:42 23/06","title":"Rashford ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/rashford-tiet-lo-niem-cam-hung-lon-nhat-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Emmanuel Petit c\u1ee7a Barca, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Argentina hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Argentina kh\u00f3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Argentina \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1  World Cup nh\u1edd Messi v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Ecuador. Tuy nhi\u00ean,  m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Messi \u0111\u00e3 che m\u1edd \u0111i s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m trong kh\u00e2u s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ed9i  h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Sampaoli. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn khi World Cup kh\u1edfi tranh, nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9. V\u00e0 Petit cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a La Albiceleste b\u00e2y gi\u1edd  kh\u00f3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Petit Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed9i \u00e1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Petit Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed9i \u00e1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Petit-Argentina-vuot-qua-vong-bang-la-mot-toi-ac-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Petit cho r\u1eb1ng Argentina kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ed1i li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i Argentina  b\u00e2y gi\u1edd qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 tin, kh\u00f4ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1eabn nhau. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng  ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 n\u1ebfu  Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. B\u1edfi v\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland.  Sampaoli th\u00ec t\u1ea1o ra qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m. Argentina t\u1eebng c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i  sao xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Argentina th\u00ec th\u1ef1c  s\u1ef1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Messi m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t \u1edf World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> t\u1ea1i Nga. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Messi, Argentina \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 chia tay gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 ghi hat-trick trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Morocco. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Messi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng penalty tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland. Anh c\u0169ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n k\u00e9m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia t\u1ea1i Nizhny Novgorod.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Jorge Sampaoli gi\u1edd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Argentina v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Iceland \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia. V\u00e0 theo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Petit, Messi c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c th\u00eam tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cMessi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Ronaldo v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00f3. Messi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMessi c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ee9c t\u1ec9nh. Khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t \u1edf Barcelona, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta t\u1eebng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u1edf Champions League. Khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng thoe \u00fd mu\u1ed1n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd t\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMessi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ee9u gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea1y m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111i b\u1ed9. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng n\u1eefa. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-argentina-03-croatia-421-189274.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Argentina 0-3 Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguyen-nhan-khien-argentina-cua-messi-tham-bai-tai-world-cup-truoc-croatia-421-189251.html\">3 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Argentina c\u1ee7a Messi th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"487","checkdouble":"189331"},{"date":"10:18 23/06","title":"L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng \"tr\u00eau ng\u01b0\u01a1i\" Serbia c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p sao Th\u1ee5y S\u0129","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/ly-giai-man-an-mung-treu-nguoi-serbia-cua-cap-sao-thuy-si.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Granit Xhaka v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri ch\u1eafp hai b\u00e0n tay l\u00e0m bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00e1nh chim sau khi s\u1eafm vai nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng gi\u00fap Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Nicholas Anelka, m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 sau ghi nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng xem ra mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a s\u00e2u xa v\u00e0 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch tr\u00eau ng\u01b0\u01a1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 Xhaka v\u00e0 Shaqiri \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 Xhaka v\u00e0 Shaqiri \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/ly-giai-man-an-mung-treu-nguoi-serbia-cua-cap-sao-thuy-si.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Xhaka v\u00e0 Shaqiri \u0103n m\u1eebng trong tr\u1eadn Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Mang qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 nh\u01b0ng Xhaka v\u00e0 Shaqiri \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c nh\u1eadp c\u01b0 t\u1eeb Albania, \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi v\u1edbi Serbia \u1edf b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Balkan. N\u00f3i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh con \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng hai \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean qu\u1ed1c k\u1ef3 Albania v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00e2y mu\u1ed1n truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p khi\u00eau kh\u00edch Serbia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Xhaka v\u00e0 Shaqiri \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a FIFA v\u00ec tuy\u00ean ng\u00f4n ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m. Ngay c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Stephan Lichtsteiner c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i: <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u cho h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n l\u1edbn lao h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. L\u1ecbch s\u1eed, chi\u1ebfn tranh \u1edf v\u00f9ng Nam T\u01b0 c\u0169 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00e0 cho qua ch\u00fat n\u00e0o h\u1ebft.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 khi t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi x\u1ebfp nh\u00ec v\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m/2 tr\u1eadn, trong khi ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n m\u1ed9t Costa Rica \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-serbia-vs-thuy-si-463-189293.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/ket-qua-serbia-vs-thuy-si.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-serbia-vs-thuy-si-463-189293.html\">Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (KT): Th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8</span><br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e9p v\u1ebf trong hi\u1ec7p 1, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"486","checkdouble":"189333"},{"date":"10:49 23/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c khi Croatia \u0111\u1ecbnh \"nh\u1ea3\" Iceland","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/nguoi-nigeria-gay-ap-luc-khi-croatia-dinh-nha-iceland.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n John Obi Mikel y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Croatia ph\u1ea3i tung ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Iceland trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng khi ngo\u00e0i Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8, t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh gi\u1eefa Argentina, Iceland v\u00e0 Nigeria. C\u1ea3 ba d\u00f9 \u00edt d\u00f9 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng mang t\u00ednh ch\u00e2t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 Argentina, Nigeria v\u00e0 Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 Argentina, Nigeria v\u00e0 Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/nguoi-nigeria-gay-ap-luc-khi-croatia-dinh-nha-iceland.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nigeria lo s\u1ee3 Iceland \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 s\u1edbm c\u1ee7a Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nigeria v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland \u0111ang l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ch\u00e2u Phi s\u1ebd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n m\u1ed9t Argentina kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i v\u00e0 v\u1ed1n tr\u00ean t\u1ea7m s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, k\u00e9o theo kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u1ea3 d\u0129 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Nigeria c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp lo\u1ea1i Argentina, sau \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd Croatia thi \u0111\u1ea5u nghi\u00eam t\u00fac tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ed \u00edt hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady sau khi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Argentina v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8, HLV Croatia \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang \u00fd ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria ch\u00fat n\u00e0o v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nigeria \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eafc kh\u00e9o h\u00f2ng t\u1ea1o \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nam \u00c2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m hay ho g\u00ec. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00ean anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. H\u00e3y t\u1ecf ra chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n nghi\u00eam t\u00fac nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dieu-gi-khien-hien-tuong-iceland-tan-chay-truoc-suc-nong-phi-chau-nigeria-421-189325.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/dieu-gi-khien-hien-tuong-iceland-tan-chay-truoc-suc-nong-phi-chau-nigeria.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dieu-gi-khien-hien-tuong-iceland-tan-chay-truoc-suc-nong-phi-chau-nigeria-421-189325.html\">\u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec khi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Iceland \u2018tan ch\u1ea3y\u2019 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u2018s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng Phi ch\u00e2u\u2019 Nigeria?</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina, \u0110T Iceland \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Nigeria thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9. V\u1eady \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"485","checkdouble":"189334"},{"date":"10:31 23/06","title":"Petit: \"Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed9i \u00e1c\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/petit-messi-khong-co-kha-nang-lanh-dao-nhu-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Emmanuel Petit c\u1ee7a Barca, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Argentina hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Argentina kh\u00f3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Argentina \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1  World Cup nh\u1edd Messi v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Ecuador. Tuy nhi\u00ean,  m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Messi \u0111\u00e3 che m\u1edd \u0111i s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m trong kh\u00e2u s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ed9i  h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Sampaoli. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn khi World Cup kh\u1edfi tranh, nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9. V\u00e0 Petit cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a La Albiceleste b\u00e2y gi\u1edd  kh\u00f3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Petit Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed9i \u00e1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Petit Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed9i \u00e1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Petit-Argentina-vuot-qua-vong-bang-la-mot-toi-ac-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Petit cho r\u1eb1ng Argentina kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ed1i li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i Argentina  b\u00e2y gi\u1edd qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 tin, kh\u00f4ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1eabn nhau. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng  ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 n\u1ebfu  Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. B\u1edfi v\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland.  Sampaoli th\u00ec t\u1ea1o ra qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m. Argentina t\u1eebng c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i  sao xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Argentina th\u00ec th\u1ef1c  s\u1ef1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Messi m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t \u1edf World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> t\u1ea1i Nga. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Messi, Argentina \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 chia tay gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 ghi hat-trick trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Morocco. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Messi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng penalty tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland. Anh c\u0169ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n k\u00e9m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia t\u1ea1i Nizhny Novgorod.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Jorge Sampaoli gi\u1edd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Argentina v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Iceland \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia. V\u00e0 theo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Petit, Messi c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c th\u00eam tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cMessi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Ronaldo v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00f3. Messi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMessi c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ee9c t\u1ec9nh. Khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t \u1edf Barcelona, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta t\u1eebng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u1edf Champions League. Khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng thoe \u00fd mu\u1ed1n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd t\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMessi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ee9u gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea1y m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111i b\u1ed9. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng n\u1eefa. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-argentina-03-croatia-421-189274.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Argentina 0-3 Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguyen-nhan-khien-argentina-cua-messi-tham-bai-tai-world-cup-truoc-croatia-421-189251.html\">3 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Argentina c\u1ee7a Messi th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"484","checkdouble":"189335"},{"date":"10:09 23/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 17h00 ng\u00e0y 23/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/nhan-dinh-slna-vs-can-tho-17h00-ngay-236-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>SLNA vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 23/6 (V\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 17h00 ng\u00e0y 236 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 17h00 ng\u00e0y 236 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/slna-cantho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">SLNA vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>SLNA vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1: 1-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede 2 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, SLNA \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1eafng khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ea1ch 8 v\u00f2ng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ch\u1ec9 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111ang kh\u00e1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 chi\u1ec1u nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, b\u1ecf c\u00e1ch khu v\u1ef1c nguy hi\u1ec3m. M\u1ecdi y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7, t\u1eeb phong \u0111\u1ed9, tinh th\u1ea7n cho t\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n b\u00e3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Vinh \u1edf V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00fang 4 b\u00e0n. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 - ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch (th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 2, thua 2 trong 6 tr\u1eadn xa nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 qua).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSLNA s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng - m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7: H\u1ed3 Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc v\u00e0 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh. Nh\u1edd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft v\u00e0 b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t c\u1ee7a V\u0103n B\u00ecnh m\u00e0 Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e2ng cao h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u nay, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i v\u00ec nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u1edf V-League 2018 (5 b\u00e0n).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu 2 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Patiyo v\u00e0 Wander Luiz (\u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng). S\u1ef1 thua thi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn SLNA tr\u1ea3i qua nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- \u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, 2 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f2a nhau v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1.<br>\r\n- SLNA b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 4 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n- 5/7 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf V-League kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ SLNA: V\u0169 H\u1ea3i \u2013 Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u00ecnh Ho\u00e0ng, V\u0103n Kh\u00e1nh, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, S\u1ef9 S\u00e2m, Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc, Xu\u00e2n Th\u1eafng, Xu\u00e2n To\u00e0n, Tu\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Olaha.<br>\r\n+ C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1: B\u00e1 S\u01a1n \u2013 Ho\u00e0ng Vissai, C\u00f4ng Th\u00e0nh, Trung Anh, \u0110\u1ee9c L\u1ed9c, T\u00f9ng Qu\u1ed1c, Quang T\u00ecnh, T\u0103ng Tu\u1ea5n, T\u1ea5n H\u00f9ng, Tambwe, Wander.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"483","checkdouble":"189336"},{"date":"10:32 23/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TPHCM vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh 18h00 ng\u00e0y 23/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/nhan-dinh-tphcm-vs-nam-dinh-18h00-ngay-236-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>TPHCM vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00fac 18h00 ng\u00e0y 23/6 (V\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TPHCM vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh 18h00 ng\u00e0y 236 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TPHCM vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh 18h00 ng\u00e0y 236 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/tphcm-nam-dinh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">TPHCM vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>TPHCM vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh: 1-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Sau 4 v\u00f2ng h\u00f2a li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i n\u1ebfm m\u00f9i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi vi\u1ebfng th\u0103m L\u1ea1ch Tray (thua 0-2). Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady 9 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Toshiya Miura v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o (h\u00f2a 4, thua 5). \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh v\u1eabn \u0111ang x\u1ebfp \u00e1p ch\u00f3t BXH v\u1edbi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 14 v\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh chi\u1ec1u nay r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. D\u00f9 c\u00f3 \u01b0u th\u1ebf s\u00e2n b\u00e3i nh\u01b0ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean TPHCM s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 (m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n/14 tr\u1eadn). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 \u1edf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Miura m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 th\u1eafng 1 (h\u00f2a 2, thua 3). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1ng khen ng\u1ee3i trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1/5 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (h\u00f2a 3, thua 1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n-\u00a0 \u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n- H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh ch\u1ec9 thua 1/5 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 1, thua 1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh: Thanh Di\u1ec7p - \u0110\u00ecnh Lu\u1eadt, \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n Robert, Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u1eefu Tu\u1ea5n, Tavares, Phi S\u01a1n, V\u0103n Thu\u1eadn, Gonzalo, Hu\u1ef3nh Kesley, Quang Nam.<br>\r\n+ Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh: Qu\u1ed1c Thi\u1ec7n Esele - Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa, H\u1eefu Qu\u00fd, H\u1ea1 Long, M\u1ea1nh C\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0110\u1ee9c Nam, H\u1eefu \u0110\u1ecbnh, S\u1ef9 Minh, Henry, Minh Tu\u1ea5n.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"482","checkdouble":"189337"},{"date":"11:00 23/06","title":"Sao s\u00e1ng Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/2/kovacic-muon-roi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic v\u1eeba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn mong mu\u1ed1n chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t.</h2><h2>Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kovacic \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid t\u1eeb Inter v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00e8 2015. Nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Zidane.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Kovacic ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 14 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i La Liga v\u00e0 Champions League cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/kovacic-muon-roi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Kovacic kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Bernabeu. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y tr\u00ean t\u1edd Marca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 r\u1eddi Real Madrid. T\u00f4i y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c. N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho MU v\u00e0 Tottenham</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/dai-gia-moi-noi-tottenham-mo-so-huu-sao-xet-cua-real-172-130926.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Kovacic</span> nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb Real Madrid t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, v\u1edbi di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Spurs kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Real th\u00eam n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1edfi trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Kovacic v\u1edbi Real c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e2m. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1edbi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Fred nh\u01b0ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n kh\u00e1c sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Fellaini v\u00e0 Carrick. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Jose Mourinho s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Do \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/toa-sang-o-world-cup-lukaku-lot-tam-ngam-real-madrid-180-189261.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup, Lukaku l\u1ecdt t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-189259.html\">Real Madrid nh\u1eafm ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"481","checkdouble":"189338"},{"date":"11:57 23/06","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 23/6: L\u00fd do Neymar b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c sau khi ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Costa Rica","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/23/ngay-hom-nay-236.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (23/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3n tin x\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c Joachim Low v\u1edbi t\u1edd SportBild, trung v\u1ec7 Mats Hummels \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00f9ng c\u1ed5 sau m\u1ed9t pha x\u1eed l\u00fd l\u00fang t\u00fang trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Hummels t\u1ef1 g\u00e2y ra cho m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 theo HLV Joachim Low, trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi g\u1eb7p \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 236 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 236 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>L\u00fd do Neymar b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c sau khi ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Costa Rica</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f3c n\u1ee9c n\u1edf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n sau khi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Brazil v\u00e0 Costa Rica vang l\u00ean. Sau \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9: \"Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. Cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng cho b\u1ea1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c. L\u00e0m t\u1ed1t l\u1eafm, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\".\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-giai-thich-ly-do-bat-khoc-sau-tran-thang-costa-rica-421-189329.html\">Neymar gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Costa Rica</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Brazil ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0103n m\u1eebng qu\u00e1 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">HLV Tite cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau tr\u1eadn Brazil - Costa Rica. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng: \u201cC\u01a1 b\u1eafp c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 s\u1ee3i c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb x\u00e9 to\u1ea1c ra. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0103n m\u1eebng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00fa ng\u00e3 c\u1ee7a Tite c\u00f3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Ederson. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Brazil c\u0169ng \u0103n m\u1eebng ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch, v\u00e0 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh x\u00f4 ng\u00e3 v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 57 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau.</div>\r\n<h2>Lukaku mu\u1ed1n \u0111o\u1ea1t c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i danh hi\u1ec7u vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV Roberto Martinez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup: \"Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Lukaku ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mong \u0111\u1ee3i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\". Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Man Utd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Panama.</div>\r\n<h2>Sterling \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh, HLV Southgate \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 Sterling. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia v\u00e0 NHM y\u00eau c\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng cho Sterling \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Southgate \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecf con n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ro-ri-doi-hinh-anh-gap-panama-sterling-lam-nguy-421-189246.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/ro-ri-doi-hinh-anh-gap-panama-sterling-lam-nguy.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ro-ri-doi-hinh-anh-gap-panama-sterling-lam-nguy-421-189246.html\">R\u00f2 r\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh g\u1eb7p Panama: Sterling l\u00e2m nguy</span><br>\r\n<span>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama v\u1eeba b\u1ecb l\u1ed9, theo \u0111\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u00e0 Southgate d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean Raheem Sterling.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00eam huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ch\u00ea Messi kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Emmanuel Petit, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00e0o hao t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1998 v\u1eeba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00ea bai Messi. Theo c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u1ec1 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh. Messi hi\u1ebfm khi \u0111\u1ee9ng ra nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed7i khi g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"480","checkdouble":"189342"},{"date":"08:40 23/06","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ebb h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t nh\u00e0 vua","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00ec l\u1ee3m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua HAGL nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 u\u1ec3 o\u1ea3i trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</h2><h2>S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1eebng &lsquo;h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t&rsquo; H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i&hellip;</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi\u1ebfn CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1edfi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eadm. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf m\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u1eabn l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u1edf ngay l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ebb h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t nh\u00e0 vua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ebb h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t nh\u00e0 vua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Du-am-HAGL-3-2-Sai-Gon-FC-Dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>S\u00e0i G\u00f2n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh qu\u1eadt c\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eb1ng 11 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfm ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch t\u1edbi 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC v\u00e0 t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ee9ng minh s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi &lsquo;h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p&rsquo; th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam trong c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd b\u1edfi t\u00ednh minh b\u1ea1ch, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t hay d\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh qua nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>&hellip; nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Pleiku c\u1ee7a HAGL v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u 22/6. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em s\u1ebd &lsquo;an to\u00e0n&rsquo; nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu thua, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p HAGL, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC r\u1ea5t khao kh\u00e1t c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t HAGL s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ra v\u1ec1 tay tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL\" title=\"HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/SG-GL6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><i>D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">90 ph\u00fat t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n thua t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao HAGL. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 nh\u1eadn ra CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1ed1n v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua chu\u1ed7i 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn hay, tr\u1eadn d\u1edf, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV T\u00e0i Em s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ec7n minh cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n tinh th\u1ea7n Iceland n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap HLV T\u00e0i Em c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1eebng cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 tham kh\u1ea3o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Iceland tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u1edb tr\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n sinh n\u0103m 1982 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c HAGL, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u1ea7n qu\u00ean chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch phi th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t v\u00e0 d\u1ed3n s\u1ee9c cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. Khi m\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh s\u1ebd tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng sau 12 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 T\u00e0i Em s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Vinh g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp su\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 SLNA. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01a1 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a t\u1edbi c\u0169ng \u0111ang hi\u1ec7n ra r\u00f5 n\u00e9t h\u01a1n v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/BXH-sau-vong-15-V-League.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>BXH V-League 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"479","checkdouble":"189318"},{"date":"07:29 23/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia (19h00 ng\u00e0y 23/6): V\u00e9 s\u1edbm cho b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/Bi-vs-Tunisia.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018: M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong t\u1ea7m tay th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Roberto Martinez \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft tranh ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ec9: Th\u1eafng to m\u00e0 v\u1eabn lo</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ec9 ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 ra, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 v\u00e0 ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng ch\u1ec9 thua ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Roberto Martinez th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh Panama ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn c\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00f4 danh v\u00e0 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec World Cup 2018, B\u1ec9 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 nh\u1edd t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Dries Mertens \u0111\u1ec3 khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia 19h00 ng\u00e0y 236 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia 19h00 ng\u00e0y 236 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Nhan-dinh-Bi-vs-Tunisia-19h00-ngay-236-bang-G-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c B\u1ec9 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn do v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0nh, \u0111\u1eb1ng n\u00e0y h\u1ecd c\u00f2n b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ebfn ba ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 k\u00e9o theo, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng suy gi\u1ea3m lu\u00f4n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1ed1n ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng s\u1ef1 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00fa vu\u1ed1t b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Mertens, ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc c\u00e1i k\u1ebft t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Martinez. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea5y th\u00ec nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, bao g\u1ed3m b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kevin De Bruyne v\u00e0 Eden Hazard, b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 thay v\u00ec duy tr\u00ec l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i pressing c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafn, h\u1ecd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i cho m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb Panama h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i, v\u1edbi 7 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Man Utd d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-30-panama-khi-moi-loi-khen-di-kem-voi-mot-chu-nhung-421-188888.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/0.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-30-panama-khi-moi-loi-khen-di-kem-voi-mot-chu-nhung-421-188888.html\">B\u1ec9&hellip; v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Panama: Khi m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi khen \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ch\u1eef &ldquo;nh\u01b0ng&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 3-0 Panama l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec l\u01b0\u1ee3t ra qu\u00e2n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i c\u00e1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u1ea5t an \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ec1 d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf v\u1eabn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t cho l\u00fac n\u00e0y, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi World Cup 2018 \u0111ang l\u00e0 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt c\u00fa s\u1ed1c kh\u00f3 tin t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Lukaku c\u0169ng c\u1edfi tr\u00f3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd cho ch\u00ednh anh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1ng nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 s\u0103n b\u00e0n cho n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd mang th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua Ph\u00e1 L\u01b0\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tunisia: Ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tunisia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ea9n s\u1ed1 th\u00fa v\u1ecb \u1edf World Cup 2018, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng h\u1ea1ng cao nh\u1ea5t FIFA (14). T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i s\u00edt sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0110\u1ea1i B\u00e0ng v\u00f9ng Carthage \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn Anh m\u01b0\u1edbt m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i h\u1ed9t trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 thua 1-2 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a Tunisia c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecd v\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3 ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd do Harry Kane, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia (19h00 ng\u00e0y 236) V\u00e9 s\u1edbm cho b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia (19h00 ng\u00e0y 236) V\u00e9 s\u1edbm cho b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Nhan-dinh-Bi-vs-Tunisia-(19h00-ngay-236)-Ve-som-cho-bay-Quy-Do-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, Anh qu\u00e1 phung ph\u00ed nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00fang h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Tunisia \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Nabil Maaloul ch\u1ec9 s\u00e2u \u0111\u1eadm trong n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai khi t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng pressing \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1edbp. Ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ecbu tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 may m\u1eafn tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Tam S\u01b0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00ec c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1edfi Anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu Harry Kane, trung phong xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec Tunisia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t n\u1ebfu ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Bi vs Tunisia\" title=\"Preview B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Bi-vs-Tunisia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0110\u1ea1i B\u00e0ng v\u00f9ng Carthage h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eeb h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng mong manh cho h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb b\u1ecf l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1eed tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tunisia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i, trong khi B\u1ec9 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng hoan ngh\u00eanh ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110\u1ea1i B\u00e0ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 ti\u1ebfp theo v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc Phi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ec9 (3-4-2-1):&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>1. Courtois;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>2. Alderweireld &ndash; 20. Boyata &ndash; 5. Vertonghen;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>15. Meunier &ndash; 7. De Bruyne &ndash; 6. Witsel &ndash; 11. Carrasco;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>14. Mertens &ndash; 10. Hazard;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>9. Lukaku<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tunisia (4-1-4-1):&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>1. Mustapha; 1<o:p></o:p>1. Bronn &ndash; 4. Meriah &ndash; 2. Youssef &ndash; 12. Maaloul;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>17. Skhiri;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>8. Youssef &ndash; 13. Sassi &ndash; 9. Badri &ndash; 23. Sliti;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>10. Khazri</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia: 2-0\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Bi vs Panama\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 vs Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Bi-vs-Panama-(3-4-2-1-vs-4-1-4-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"478","checkdouble":"189324"},{"date":"08:37 23/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico (22h ng\u00e0y 23/6): \"Chi\u1ebfn binh Teageuk\" v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/nhan-dinh-han-quoc-vs-mexico-22h-ngay-236-chien-binh-teageuk-ve-nuoc-som.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mexico \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sau kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc M\u0129 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out ngay sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn h\u00f4m nay.</h2><h2>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu \u1edbt</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i World Cup. Sau khi th\u00fac th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Mexico kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0i to\u00e1n \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Kh\u00e2u ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c &ldquo;chi\u1ebfn binh Taegeuk&rdquo; \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. V\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 12 trong 13 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico (22h ng\u00e0y 236) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico (22h ng\u00e0y 236) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Han-quoc-vs-mexico.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n trong 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng cho H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i trong 3 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n \u1edf World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc. HLV Uli Stielike \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c1. HLV Shin Tae-yong l\u00ean thay nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-0. May m\u1eafn cho H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111\u1ebfn Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Son Heung-min l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup ph\u1ea3i e d\u00e8.</div>\r\n<h2>Mexico \u0111ang tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang g\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u00e1y th\u00ec Mexico l\u1ea1i tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>, El Tri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c virus c\u00fam \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f9ng ph\u00e1t \u1edf tr\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mexico \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0y binh b\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. H\u1ecd lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd thay v\u00ec co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Mexico \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 World Cup v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hirving Lozano la hien tuong moi cua bong da Mexico.\" title=\"Hirving Lozano l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Mexico.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/giai-ma-hirving-lozano-el-chucky-ke-thich-gieo-rac-noi-so-hai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mexico c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft World Cup 2018 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t La-tinh trong m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u, Mexico gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng. El Tri \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 hi\u1ec7u h\u00f3a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Mexico \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc M\u0129 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t gi\u1eefa kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ef1u binh d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Guardado, Vela, Chicharito hay Ochoa v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a El Tri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang nh\u01b0 Salcedo, Gallardo v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Lozano. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c, sao tr\u1ebb Lozano \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o \u0111ang gi\u00fap anh l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG H\u00e0 Lan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, vi\u1ec7c Mexico gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn x\u1ea3y ra, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o th\u1ebf ch\u00e2n t\u01b0\u1eddng. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0o c\u0169ng d\u1edf t\u1ec7 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico:</strong><br>\r\n- L\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1998, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc M\u0129 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 3-1<br>\r\n- H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 12 trong 13 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi trong 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp<br>\r\n- H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng trong 7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup, thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp<br>\r\n- Mexico gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup khi g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c1<br>\r\n- Mexico m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 thua 2 trong 18 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup<br>\r\n- Mexico ch\u01b0a th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2002<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Han Quoc vs Mexico\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Han-Quoc-vs-Mexico-(4-3-3-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1: 0-2</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/son-heungmin-tu-hy-vong-tro-thanh-that-vong-421-188946.html\">Son Heung-min: T\u1eeb hy v\u1ecdng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018-421-188894.html\">3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"477","checkdouble":"189327"},{"date":"08:48 23/06","title":"\u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (01h00 ng\u00e0y 24/6): Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/23/duc-vs-thuy-dien-01h00-ngay-246-them-mot-bat-ngo.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i, Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c phong \u0111\u1ed9. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2>\u0110KV\u0110 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m khi b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 0-1, nh\u01b0ng \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 n\u00e9t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">So v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i Confed Cup c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Die Mannschaft s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n em. Joachim Low, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft b\u00e0i v\u1edf, v\u00e0 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc to\u00e0n t\u1eadp \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, trong khi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c h\u1edf ra nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3. Theo <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te-465-188763.html\" target=\"_blank\">trung v\u1ec7 Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico</span>, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00f2n 1-2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u00ec <strong>&ldquo;ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 b\u1eb1ng m\u1eaft \u00e0?&rdquo;</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/DKVD-Duc-thua-soc-ngay-ra-quan-Low-da-thuc-su-het-bai-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng \u01b0ng \u00fd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Thomas Muller. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Bayern \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1eaft Joshua Kimmich ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh c\u1ea3 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb lao h\u1eb3n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ec3 tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, b\u1edfi Muller kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. H\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3, c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Kimmich \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Joachim Low c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. H\u1ecd qu\u00e1 n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 m\u00e0 tung t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi r\u00fat lu\u00f4n Khedira ra ngo\u00e0i. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, Mexico kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t, v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa (ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n duy nh\u1ea5t Kroos \u0111\u00e1 trung t\u00e2m).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Joachim Low ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0110KV\u0110 ti\u1ebfp theo b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Low\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/duc3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Low c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Janne Andersson \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u tay tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u1eafm ch\u00fat l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng F. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 Mexico, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, khi h\u1ecd&hellip; ch\u1eb3ng h\u01a1n g\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ibrahimovic, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. N\u00ean nh\u1edb, HLV Andersson to\u00e0n quy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ibra, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u00ec mu\u1ed1n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, nh\u01b0ng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Mexico l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft tay nhau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo (trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p El Tri h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c). \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ra chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/3-yeu-to-khien-DT-Han-Quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u tay t\u1ea1i World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Die Mannschaft ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian qu\u00e1 d\u00e0i \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng. \u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m, m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a Joachim Low, v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ed7 v\u00e0i nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng Kimmich v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd lao l\u00ean b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nguy hi\u1ec3m ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Janne Andersson s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u0169i c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Emil Forsberg &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Bundesliga. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, anh hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a Kimmich, v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd khai th\u00e1c tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Hirving Lozano c\u1ee7a Mexico \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u m\u00e0 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f4i khi khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd c\u00e0ng th\u00eam b\u1ed1i r\u1ed1i. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Preview \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/duc-vs-thuy-dien-01h00-ngay-246-them-mot-bat-ngo.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- \u0110\u1ee9c thua Mexico m\u1edbi l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2 trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup, sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m 1982. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, tin t\u00edch c\u1ef1c l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 11 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 40 n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1o ra 16 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 2 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (4-4, 5-3).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- \u0110\u1ee9c ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn trong 4 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Muller ghi 10 b\u00e0n sau 14 c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 5 l\u1ea7n trong 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eebng ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n 2 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3 (Italia 1950 v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c 1958).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng sau 402 ph\u00fat li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Joachim Low c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf r\u01a1i Ozil tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Marcos Reus \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Hummels c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf c\u1ed5, trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sami Khedira c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i, sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Ilkay Gundogan, ho\u1eb7c Leon Goretzka.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean ph\u00eda Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man United &ndash; Victor Lindelof \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1ecfi \u1ed1m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 5\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Nhan-dinh-Duc-vs-Thuy-Dien-bang-F-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: 1-1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 6\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/F.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-ay-la-zlatan-nhung-chung-ta-la-thuy-dien-421-188871.html\">Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 Zlatan, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018-461-188852.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lozano-ghi-ban-ha-guc-duc-mot-cdv-mexico-bat-ngo-lay-duoc-vo-421-188930.html\">Lozano ghi b\u00e0n h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110\u1ee9c, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Mexico b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ee3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-world-cup-2018-h1-461-188750.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/duc-thua-soc-mexico-ngay-ra-quan-khong-som-canh-tinh-loi-nguyen-nha-dkvd-se-linh-ung-421-188770.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c thua s\u1ed1c Mexico: Kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh, l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 s\u1ebd linh \u1ee9ng!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"476","checkdouble":"189328"},{"date":"02:28 23/06","title":"HLV Iceland v\u1eabn m\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 \u1edf World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-iceland-van-mo-dieu-than-ky-o-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Hallgrimsson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 51 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u khi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Iceland ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018, Iceland \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Argentina 1-1. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Vi\u1ec7c Argentina thua Croatia 0-3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Iceland th\u1eafp s\u00e1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hallgrimsson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Hallgrimsson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/HLV-Hallgrimsson-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Nigeria-vs-Iceland-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Iceland \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nigeria 0-2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 n\u1ebfu Iceland \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Hallgrimsson \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t khi d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 1.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nSang hi\u1ec7p 2 khi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng Iceland kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng so v\u1edbi Nigeria, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i chung cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-cua-nigeria-truoc-iceland-421-189312.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Nigeria vs Iceland</span> vinh danh Musa, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n cho \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u201d. V\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Iceland tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Hallgrimsson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 51 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u khi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Heimir Hallgrimsson cung la mot nha si.\" title=\"HLV Heimir Hallgrimsson c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nha s\u0129.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Heimir-Hallgrimsson.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Heimir Hallgrimsson tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Iceland s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi Iceland \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong hi\u1ec7p 1 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t trong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n gi\u00fap Nigeria gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Iceland l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1eb9p, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u khi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Croatia v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cIceland \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 \u1edf Euro 2016 khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c \u1edf World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)<br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"475","checkdouble":"189313"}]}